          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Safe Equitable Campus Resources and Education Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to address the needs of individuals with disabilities, such as their needs if a campus is evacuated or their needs if they are victims of sex offenses, domestic violence, dating violence and stalking incidents. </p>]]></text>
